name: NYDailyNews
text:
Rhode Island mailed out 176 tax refund checks carrying Mickey Mouse’s signature on lines meant for the the general treasurer and state controller.

The misprints occurred due to a “technical error” and have been voided.
https://t.co/FLjBIUZssS

name: NYDailyNews
text:
Oklahoma man caught a world-record 150-pound paddlefish — breaking the record set last month in the same lake.

The fish was first caught in 1997 when it was 2 years old as part of a research effort by an Oklahoma State grad student.
https://t.co/H5S4kX8aml

name: NYDailyNews
text:
Suzyn Waldman made good on a years-long promise to Gerrit Cole to sing the National Anthem after telling him he'd one day be a great Yankee.

Waldman has sung the national anthem many times before, but this one was special.
https://t.co/3YlhOjCElP
